  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $3300<br />Duration: 3-6 months</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri office hours</p><p>Location: Tanjong Pagar</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>•\tResponsible for planning, coordinating and delivery of office improvement and relocation works.</p><p>•\tCoordinating with consultants, contractors overseeing project governance and driving workplace transformation</p><p>•\tConduct engagement sessions, briefings and workplace feedback surveys</p><p>•\tAble to handle digital tools (video, infographics, visuals etc) for communications & engagement</p><p>•\tAble to handle end-to-end project delivery</p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in any course w min 2 yrs of relevant experience in administrative roles</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p>allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>",
